Real Funeral Insurance -
it's one simple thing you can do
to ease the burden on your family
PAYA
AEALN
BACK
UARI
PANTEN
All it takes is one
simple phone call
It's easy to protect your family from the cost
of your funeral and other final expenses with
Real Guaranteed Funeral Insurance.
Now with our Real Payback Guarantee, your
family will also have financial certainty that
the payout they receive will always be the
Benefit Amount or the total premiums paid
- whichever is more!
✓ Your family will receive a quick cash
payment of up to $15,000' when they
need it the most
Australian residents aged 18-79 are
guaranteed cover - with no medical or
blood test
You will also get back 10% of the
premiums you have paid after the first 12
months of your policy
H7509_Real_WD_FI_03/17
Plus...
Free Will Kit with your policy!
Get a quote today!
Call 1300 128 047
or visit realinsurance.com.au
Benefit paid for Accidental Death only in the first 12 months
If your policy is cancelled and cover ends, no Benefit Amount is payable and there are no premium refunds after the cooling off period.
If you change your cover your premium and eligibility for the Real Payback Guarantee may be affected. This is general information only.
Please consider the PDS available from realinsurance.com.au. This information is provided by Real Insurance a trading name of Greenstone

ABN 37 062 395 484. Terms and conditions apply
